reviewText: This first season was just okay, Dan Castellaneta was great as the voice of Doc, but the character Jennifer Parker doesn't get on screen credit until Season 2, so it's unknown whether it's Cathy Cavadini or someone else playing her.  I hate it when roles go to waste.
If you like the movies and cartoons, this is a must have.
My son loves anything to do with back to the future!
Great, fun cartoon for my son who loves all things Back to the Future.
Great dvd show must have for any back to the future fan
